                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220522-53-off285 t18220522-53-cd286"></join>, 1 lb. 13 ozs. of tea, value 6 s.
            </rs>, the goods of the 
               <persName id="t18220522-53-victim491" type="victimName">
                     <rs id="t18220522-53-viclabel287" type="occupation">United Company of Merchants, trading to the East Indies</rs>
